Megatron looked at Hun-grr, then Motormaster. He was a bit curious as to
what was wrong with Motormaster, but it had to wait. He began to pace.
"Decepticons, our base is not in a safe area, and to fix that, Hun-grr
and Motormaster will take their sub-groups, and follow Astrotrain,
Stratus, and Cyclonus to the Azores Islands. When there, Astrotrain will
give the orders." Megatron said calmly.
